headline: Georgia Power, Atlanta Falcons team up for Light Up the Holidays contest
summary: Georgia Power and the Atlanta Falcons are teaming up to spread holiday spirit through Georgia Power's Light Up the Holidays Contest. From Nov. 28 through Dec. 12, customers are invited to share how they're "lighting up the holidays" – either with festive decorations or acts of community service – by entering the Light Up the Holidays Contest.
